002package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.node;
003
004import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.format.IPathFormatter;
005
006//REFACTOR: Check if this is used, delete?
007public interface IAssemblyInstanceGroupedNodeItem
008    extends IAssemblyNodeItem {
009
010  @Override
011  default String format(IPathFormatter formatter) {
012    return formatter.formatAssembly(this);
013  }
014
015  @Override
016  default IAssemblyInstanceGroupedNodeItem getNodeItem() {
017    return this;
018  }
019
020  @Override
021  default <CONTEXT, RESULT> RESULT accept(INodeItemVisitor<CONTEXT, RESULT> visitor, CONTEXT context) {
022    return visitor.visitAssembly(this, context);
023  }
024}
